            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"so-cpr-data-exploration\">SO-CPR Data Exploration</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Explores the abundance data before LDA:</span>\n<ol>\n<li>Taxon-level sparsity and skewness</li>\n<li>Segment-level total abundance distribution</li>\n<li>Pinkerton log-normalisation preview</li>\n<li>LDA model selection metrics (Gensim K=2\u201330)</li>\n</ol></span>"
