            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"3-total-abundance-distribution\">3. Total Abundance Distribution</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Comparing raw total abundance per segment vs. segment-length-corrected\nlog concentration (Pinkerton normalisation).</span></span>"
