            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"4-pinkerton-log-normalisation\">4. Pinkerton Log-Normalisation</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Per Pinkerton et al. (2020): for each taxon, log-transform the\nsegment-length-corrected concentration where present, keeping zeros as-is.\nAdds a presence/absence indicator column for each taxon.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
