            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"5-lda-model-selection-gensim-k230\">5. LDA Model Selection (Gensim, K=2\u201330)</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Vertical lines mark the 4 candidate K values: <strong>3, 7, 10, 16</strong>.</span>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Perplexity</strong> \u2014 lower = better fit (\u4f46\u53ef\u80fd overfit)</li>\n<li><strong>Coherence (c_v)</strong> \u2014 higher = more interpretable topics</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
